{"tid":1458163,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一間本土品牌茶飲店既心聲","createTime":"2019-08-12T13:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T06:36:22.000Z","uid":304230,"like":166,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"b79c4a0045c78bdd107b395e62bda967494312c2","tid":1458163,"uid":304230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:08:12.000Z","msg":"唔知大家仲記唔記得我<br />\n由於之前比連仔bam左ac 依家先開得返<br />\n終於可以出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地唔係咩大公司大品牌<br />\n我地係本土品牌既茶飲店<br />\n如果你問我點解做本土？<br />\n我可以答你係因為我地係香港人！<br />\n好愛香港呢個地方！！<br />\n相信呢兩個月發生左咩事大家都有眼睇<br />\n而我地呢個星期係尖沙咀亦見到唔小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實點解香港會演變成咁？<br />\n就係因為政府唔去回應我地<br />\n點解林鄭一個人既決定<br />\n要整個香港幫你受罪？<br />\n夠膽講壽終正寢 點解唔夠膽講撒回？<br />\n夠膽講警察無做錯 <br />\n點解唔夠膽成立獨立調查委員會？<br />\n係因為警黑合作！？<br />\n混入左公安！？<br />\n槍槍打頭！？<br />\n人在做 天在看！等天收啦！！過街老鼠！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地係全力支持遊行集會表達訴求 <br />\n<br />\n經過我地商討後決定 <br />\n想盡我地既能力去出一分力<br />\n<br />\n如果有需要 我地會無限量提供<br />\n<br />\n-乾糧<br />\n-水<br />\n-生理鹽水<br />\n-急救用品<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有需要就入黎啦 唔洗怕羞！<br />\n(生理鹽水同急救用品暫時得尖沙咀店有)<br />\n<br />\n亦都想話比大家知 依家經濟真係好差<br />\n罷買唔緊要 最緊要繼續支持香港本土小店<br />\n相信佢地做得本土品牌都同我地一樣<br />\n係好愛香港架！！<br />\n如果你地都唔支持 香港可能會無哂本土野<br />\n希望大家可以一齊共度難關！！<br />\n香港人 加油！！<br />\n<br />\n最後想同林鄭講<br />\n<br />\nIf We Burn, You Burn With Us！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6500a0729a8e458f2aa8b464de41a084089afb8","tid":1458163,"uid":1707,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"唇茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc436e8e509850bc23a99e503d2d88641f65f52","tid":1458163,"uid":152262,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:19:18.000Z","msg":"相由心生 樓主真係好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb1d17ddaf8cb540905038e46b8fe7cdd10421f","tid":1458163,"uid":42446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"同熱愛這片土地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89cbec301a5560ae79d16ea5872521650bb39ad","tid":1458163,"uid":111181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:27:08.000Z","msg":"你好呀樓豬"},{"pid":"484a0a02cb75624e0b470027e2cc34b1efe1f1d0","tid":1458163,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T15:33:32.000Z","msg":"樓主好靚仔"},{"pid":"117f10a0784a5e30ff45f61c3fdb89ecf3928c08","tid":1458163,"uid":104669,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"樓主好靚仔<br />\n樓主個frd仲靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb1f8fa69db2d94cc3feaecd20b1352ea90712d","tid":1458163,"uid":190197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T20:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5543749f1e4fc72e0a02341bbfb60e1149c8b639","tid":1458163,"uid":68661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae635fad7bf38a5f8cf8e203d66eaa10082219d","tid":1458163,"uid":51657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019